{"type": "article", "id": 47930, "title": "Kanye West 被起诉，以及，有一款可以行走的智能行李箱 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-12-05T04:16:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2381, "name": "行李箱"}, {"id": 46060, "name": "YEEZY"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 13476, "name": "OTB"}, {"id": 7113, "name": "Kanye West"}, {"id": 18566, "name": "Daniel Arsham"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171205104624jFEuwoK8akNM2P7T.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/517049\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>时尚集团 OTB 人事重组，将强化品牌改革</strong></a> | 旗下拥有 Diesel、Maison Margiela、Marni 等多个品牌的 OTB 集团，日前宣布将起用 Ubaldo Minelli 为 CEO，Carlo Schiavo 为 CFO。目前，Diesel 是集团最核心的品牌，约占 60% 的份额，但从 2016 年开始品牌在北美、欧洲等地的业绩持续下滑，OTB 有意进行品牌重塑，推进改革。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.thefashionlaw.com/home/kanye-west-slapped-with-new-lawsuit-over-yeezy-season-garments\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>因为未按合同支付佣金，Kanye West 被起诉</strong></a> | 据 The Fashion of Law 称，土耳其代理人 Derya Gulseven 对 Kanye West 提出诉讼，要求支付 22.8 万美元的佣金。Derya Gulseven 自 2015 年起被 West Brands 雇佣，为其生产的 Yeezy 系列在土耳其寻找服饰材料。在 Yeezy 2 系列服装预定交货期前，West Brands 的合同无故中断，Derya Gulseven 仍在几个月后为 Yeezy 3 工作，但品牌并未给出“相应的佣金”。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/media/w-magazine-positions-itself-as-a-luxury-collectible-11060539/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>康泰纳仕集团旗下的 W Magazine 重新调整</strong></a> | 2018 年起，W Magazine 将由每年发行 11 期改为 8 期，同时，杂志的价格也将从 7.99 美元上涨为 9.99 美元。W Magazine 的主编 Stefano Tonchi 称，这是顺应时代变化的举措，杂志将会变成爱好者们收藏的漂亮商品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111817p57gURVfsvxWziuF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>之前和 adidas 合作过很多次，还为它打造过“蓝色庭园”的美国艺术家 Daniel Arsham，最近再度联手 adidas ，推出了一双带有 Ultra Boost 大底的 Adidas Originals，这双全灰色的鞋子面料也很特殊，由 Daniel Arsham 亲自挑选。他称它为“<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/12/04/daniel-arsham-snarkitecture-materials-adidas-originals-present-shoes-sneakers/\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约礼物</a>”。 </p><p>这双鞋将于 12 月 8 日率先登陆 KITH 迈阿密店。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111853i9H2xDnWIjrLP3Ns.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111843HgDvmyWEsFnQNO39.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.751761\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111843dBlbYhzGVt1UngKP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.751174\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111845L1Vn3NUOA7lRxTzp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.751174\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051118494DUT5CBL3hadvcSt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.751761\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2017/12/coach-pre-fall-2018-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coach 2018 早春系列</a>出炉，创意总监 Stuart Vevers 称它是“诞生于纽约，美式哥特童话”。好不好看另说，但确实花哨又热闹。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111925WqMSmcsi7IBaTvEO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051119265VQRwFzX3iZlkuKJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111926nvQ2bUNCzlMhK3o8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111928rzuVLKYp5lgO7j1P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111931DIsxXdTiC5YR39JU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051119335wg8f2yMAW3QLK9R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111934KtZbjuwD4Yh3liIN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111935U2mI4wzZCKejTgkV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111937d6WeSjipnbVAlZ90.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111938vx18YqBfMT7ZsDiS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111940oXJWa1YdhF0D9tBj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111944TOBLIr8KXVWMPjpm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111947a1WVoLRlpdCfhKby.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051119484tKEq3yowZAX5RBO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111948VTl8MLeYh2rWoxgB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111949oNxnCR9iPUjsIBzt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111950o6WN8xlrpZBmcGHT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111953iFbvketP4UM8jQqf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111953lTEVohbczDkYXsf9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205111957djz1EAp7K6luVs8f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112000fD20pY9KMtcIwo7F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/jil-sander-mario-sorrenti-t-shirts/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jil Sander 与著名的时尚摄影师 Mario Sorrenti 合作发布联名系列</a>。Sorrenti 凭借为美国和意大利版《Vogue》和《Harper's Bazaar》拍摄的极富挑逗意味的专题大片而成名，Jil Sander 的这次合作款直接就把他拍摄的写真印在了 T 恤上。 </p><p>该系列 T 恤目前已登陆 colette，单价 490 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112030Y7uSn5ChKZciG96k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112030A94P6cMKpu7dU1fE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051120309sQ2JArIytHguvY5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051120305ORYrNlEqhDbgwZW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112030y0NMjQ7mepioXuWO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112031gK7IOAc8zF2BsDpC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112031XQ5eM7UD3L2iBam8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112031p9dEJ4aFzQcB7wbK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112031fJjrKLnWNoDR8BU2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>PUMA 发售全新女鞋系列<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-12-04/puma-2018ss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> PUMA Muse Echo</a>，每双售价 130 美元。代言人是 Cara Delevingne。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112047k79CDv0HcN5w4ijm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051120468lShO3zLnosUD6Wu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112049rBGPybZJLF7WQcE1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>可以自己走的行李箱机器人<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-12-05/travelmate/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Travelmate </a>公布了发售信息。这款特殊的行李箱安装了 Follow Me 的用户感应系统，充满电最多可以用 4 个小时，时速高达 9 千米，它可以通过 GPS 与对应的手机 app 相连进行管理。可以横着走也可以竖着走，还有三个不同的尺寸大小和多重颜色配置。 </p><p>Travelmate 售价 126000 日元，将于明年四月正式在日本发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112253yEH0iaNQce8D9PFs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562121\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112253YqMAkpOguoXne4QB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562121\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112253xm6J8Hf14h2UF7di.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.756061\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112252xpmHVdT8wQNFnOSL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.696970\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051122579vPJyZlFm03UIChe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562121\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112258SexT1OhPq3CgkfzN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.460606\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112252VuXsgKcI4aPmLwHR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707576\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112252oL6cdPD0Qkpwn83X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.680303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112257yzL4TrF5igONGeAn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.110000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171205112258shxouSIbXGn4v9O3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.975758\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201712051122598AwR4lihU9yQrFdS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.975758\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Kanye West</p>"}